      "side": 1,
      "message": "crashpad_is_fuchsia is when the code is being run on fuchsia.\ncrashpad_is_in_fuchsia is when the code is being built inside the fuchsia tree, rather than standalone, or in Chromium.\n\nSo for situations you care about, they\u0027re probably both set to true. I would expect probably crashpad_is_fuchsia is correct, but I\u0027m not sure what hermetic_deps actually does.\n\nThat said, mig is Mac/mach-only isn\u0027t it? What does this have to do with Fuchsia?",
