      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ah, thanks Scott, I think we want crashpad_is_in_fuchsia.\n\nFor context, we\u0027re trying to improve the hermeticity of our build by tracing actions and making sure they only touch their declared inputs and outputs (see https://fuchsia.dev/fuchsia-src/development/build/hermetic_actions?hl\u003den).\n\nThis particular action appears to touch files outside of its declared deps (https://ci.chromium.org/ui/p/turquoise/builders/global.dev.ci/core.x64-vg-debug-mac-build_default/b8856463748019187504/overview), so we need to exclude it from action tracing. That\u0027s what the `hermetic_deps \u003d false` label does.",
